    public class UIXInputPopup
extends PartialUIXInputPopup
    UIXInputPopup is a base abstraction for components that allow both input and selection from a list of possible values.

    Events:

    Type Phases Description
    oracle.adf.view.rich.event.SelectionEvent Apply Request Values The valueChange event is delivered when the value attribute is changed.
